# Extglob patterns in case statements
# Extended glob patterns @(), ?(), *(), +(), !() must be handled

=== basic @() extglob
# @extglob
case $x in @(a|b)) echo match;; esac
---
(case (word "$x") (pattern ((word "@(a|b)")) (command (word "echo") (word "match"))))
---


